{"_path":"/eng/e029","_dir":"eng","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"AI筆記本 - Google NotebookLM","description":null,"image":"/images/e028-01.jpeg","sequence":28,"category":"8. AI智能助理","link":null,"author":null,"head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 Security Notes"},{"name":"og:title","content":"HR"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-10-07T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"ai-筆記本-google-notebooklm"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AI 筆記本 - Google NotebookLM"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://notebooklm.google.com/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Google NotebookLM"}]},{"type":"text","value":" Website"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"reference"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Reference"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1jdo3xemlSs"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AI 筆記神器 NotebookLM "}]},{"type":"text","value":" Gemini 1.5 Pro 加持，整理筆記、論文閱讀、資訊統整超輕鬆！還能直接問答　打造你的個人知識庫！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.playpcesor.com/2024/06/google-notebooklm-ai.html"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Google NotebookLM 免費中文 AI 筆記實例教學，老師、學生、創作者利器"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/80532/google-notebooklm-audio-overview"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Google 自學神器"}]},{"type":"text","value":"！上傳資料到 NotebookLM 可一鍵生成「模擬 podcast"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"EV 實驗室: "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YKN-2CQ2N5g"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Google 出品 AI 笔记应用 NotebookLM"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YmVZkl6KVUs"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Best Ways to use NotebookLM (over Perplexity) for Content Research"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"notebook-lm-的應用案例"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Notebook LM 的應用案例"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"快速總結長文"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"回答複雜問題"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"激發新的靈感"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"整理資料"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"notebook-lm-特色與功能"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Notebook LM 特色與功能"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"NotebookLM 會反映 Google 文件或簡報中更新的內容嗎？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n將 Google 文件或簡報匯入 NotebookLM 後，我們會製作原始 Google 文件的副本並上傳至 NotebookLM。上傳完成後，NotebookLM 不會自動追蹤檔案的更新內容，包括存取權在內。NotebookLM 無法刪除或編輯原始檔案。你必須手動重新上傳本機檔案，或點選「按一下即可與 Google 雲端硬碟保持同步」按鈕，重新整理已匯入來源檢視器的 Google 文件和簡報。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在 NotebookLM 中，來源的檔案大小上限是多少？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n目前的限制為每個來源最多 500,000 字，頁面數量沒有限制。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"NotebookLM 支援哪些語言？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nNotebookLM 目前支援超過 35 種語言。你可以在 Google 帳戶的設定中變更語言偏好設定。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"NotebookLM 是否支援 PDF？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n是，NotebookLM 支援 PDF，但有限制："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"內容只有圖片的 PDF：自 2024 年 9 月起，我們將進一步支援內容只有圖片的 PDF。NotebookLM 會改善 PDF 內圖片的處理方式，但你可能要重新上傳先前匯入的 PDF。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如要讓 NotebookLM 提供來源的內容摘要，有哪些好方法？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nNotebookLM 提供兩種摘要來源的方式：你可以直接透過對話要求提供來源中特定主題內容的摘要，也可以在左側來源檢視器中點選來源開啟「來源指南」，NotebookLM 就會自動生成整個來源內容的摘要。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果想在對話中要求提供更具體的摘要，請試試下列方式："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"針對所需資訊提出具體問題。如果選取多個來源，請試著在查詢中加入來源名稱，讓 NotebookLM 縮小搜尋範圍。舉例來說，你可以試試「請根據名稱為〈犬隻訓練概論〉的來源文件，概述當中有關犬隻訓練的重要研究結果」，而不是「概述這個來源」。\n我可以與其他人即時協同編輯筆記嗎？\n當然可以！記事會即時顯示所有協作者的編輯內容。如果你和其他人開啟同一個筆記本，只要有人修改筆記本內容，其他人也會看到這些變更。只有具備共用筆記本「編輯者」身分的使用者，才能編輯記事。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"為什麼 NotebookLM 有時會表示無法回答問題？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nNotebookLM 無法回答問題的可能原因如下："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"安全性標記"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：來源中可能含有會觸發安全性標記的內容。如果來源中有暴力、情色或猥褻等敏感主題，就可能會發生這種情況，即使是歷史類內容也一樣。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"表達不清楚"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：請試著換個說法，更明確或更具體地說明問題。如果筆記本含有大量來源 (超過 LLM 的脈絡窗口大小)，NotebookLM 必須先根據問題擷取最相關的資訊，再嘗試使用這些資訊生成回覆。你的問題越具體，NotebookLM 就更能找出相關資訊。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"來源中沒有相關資訊"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：NotebookLM 的設計是根據上傳來源的資訊回答問題。如果在來源資料找不到答案，NotebookLM 就無法回覆。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"透過網址匯入來源時，NotebookLM 如何處理含有互動元素的 HTML 來源？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n系統只會匯入網頁上顯示的文字，我們正在改善這類匯入內容的處理方式。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"回覆提示時，NotebookLM 如何使用來源、對話內容和記事？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"記事"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：只在選取時使用。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"來源"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：一律使用，無論是所有來源或你選取的個別來源。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"對話記錄"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：生成回覆時也會使用這類資料。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"ai-筆記本-google-notebooklm","depth":2,"text":"AI 筆記本 - Google NotebookLM","children":[{"id":"reference","depth":3,"text":"Reference"},{"id":"notebook-lm-的應用案例","depth":3,"text":"Notebook LM 的應用案例"},{"id":"notebook-lm-特色與功能","depth":3,"text":"Notebook LM 特色與功能"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:eng:e029.md","_source":"content","_file":"eng/e029.md","_extension":"md"}